NEW GAME FEATURES:

	FRIENDLY MATCH
		Endpoint : /api/game/friendly-match
		Method : GET
		Response : Room ID (Guaranteed)
		Where : Chatroom, When user clicks new button "Challenge"
		Behavior : Create a sessionStorage similar to Matchmaking, then redirect to online Client.
				   Also send to friend a clickable message. When clicked :
				   Query /api/game/available/:id for a Boolean
				       if true:
				   			Create a sessionStorage similar to Matchmaking, then redirect to online Client.
					   else
					   		Show ToastInfo : "Room is no Longer Available."

	SPECTATE
		Endpoint : /api/game/spectate
		Method : GET
		Response : Room ID  OR  roomId : null if no rooms to spectate
		Where : Dashboard Spectate Button (Previously Join Room)
		Behavior : Create a sessionStorage similar to Matchmaking, then redirect to online Client.
				   OR
				   If roomId is null, inform User: "There are No Matches to Spectate!"


SESSION STORAGE FORMAT REMINDER:

interface RoomData
{
	roomId:			string;
	PlayerID:		string;
	playerName: 	string | null;   <== if null default to empty string
	playerAvatar:	string | null;	 <== if null default to "/game/Assets/default.png"
}

sessionStorage.setItem("room", JSON.stringify(roomData));